video.title: Workin' Moms
video.synopsis: Maternity leave is over and it's time for these four moms to return to work while navigating kids, bosses, love and life in modern-day Toronto.

episodes.synopsis: Kate returns to her advertising agency after maternity leave and discovers two people hired in her absence. Frankie experiences postpartum disorder.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Kate juggles date night, pumping and a competitive co-worker. Erotic fiction and IT collide in Jenny's workplace. Anne's daughter is out of control.
episodes.title: Rules

episodes.synopsis: Frankie needs help. The ladies discuss playing "the girl card." Grandma and formula enter Kate's house. Anne deals with her disobedient daughter.
episodes.title: Fem Card

episodes.synopsis: Kate's mom dislikes the dog but loves the baby. Anne hires an expert mean girl. Ian grates as a stay-at-home dad, but Jenny finds calm at work.
episodes.title: Bad Help

episodes.synopsis: It's decision time for Kate and Olly. Anne gets jealous of Mean Nanny. Frankie finds a hobby. Jenny feels disconnected from baby Zoe.
episodes.title: Sophie's Choice-ish

episodes.synopsis: Frankie shops for a toy. Kate has a new deadline and a Japanese porn fetish. Jenny connects with Marvin, but at what cost?
episodes.title: The Wolf and the Rabbit

episodes.synopsis: Frankie finally scores. Anne spends time with her daughter. Ian turns the camera on Jenny. Kate is shocked after handing the reins to a junior staffer.
episodes.title: Phoenix Rising

episodes.synopsis: Kate launches a nanny search. Frankie and Giselle work on their relationship. Jenny plans an ambitious bachelorette party.
episodes.title: Popsicle and a Hoop Earring

episodes.synopsis: Kate and Nathan disagree on babies and a temporary work assignment. Financial issues force Anne to see extra clients. Jenny has a nipple infection.
episodes.title: Tricky Nipple

episodes.synopsis: Kate lies to a mom group and feels guilty about her choice. Frankie has no option but to deal with her depression. A doctor orders Anne to slow down.
episodes.title: The Coxswain

episodes.synopsis: Kate preps for a long trip. Jenny continues to spiral out of control. Frankie discovers Marie Kondo. Anne dreams of visiting a new type of doctor.
episodes.title: Bye Bye Kate

episodes.synopsis: Kate wakes up refreshed in Montreal. Jenny makes up with her work friend. Frankie masters online sales. Anne and Lionel face a difficult choice.
episodes.title: Merde

episodes.synopsis: Kate shows off her skills of persuasion while Nathan fights a diaper rash. Frankie gets an ultimatum. Jenny tells Ian the truth. Anne finds peace.
episodes.title: Finale

episodes.synopsis: It's 2005 and a young, ambitious Kate attends her best friend Anne's expensive wedding. That night kicks off a series of life-changing events.
Kate's forced hiatus from Gaze grates at her working-mom soul. Anne researches a vasectomy for Lionel. Frankie loves the women's wellness center.
episodes.title: Good Mom

episodes.synopsis: Kate mourns a death in unexpected ways. A jarring event makes Frankie reconsider a job. Ian finds luck with his screenplay. Lionel goes into overdrive.
episodes.title: The Sign

episodes.synopsis: Kate tries to balance two jobs. Frankie finds herself attracting lots of different women. Anne moves into her new office and runs into an old flame.
episodes.title: The Holy Hole

episodes.synopsis: Ian asks for permission and Sonia grants it. Anne lies down for hypnotherapy. An intervention leads Kate to loosen up at Baseline even as Gaze calls.
episodes.title: Consent

episodes.synopsis: Kate's two-job juggle has unexpected consequences. Stressed about her ex, Anne picks a fight with Kate. Frankie embraces new hair and a new home.
episodes.title: Shame Spiral

episodes.synopsis: The members of Val's Toddler Time group attend a weekend retreat. Ian discovers a sexual issue. Kate and Anne still disagree. One mom has a breakdown.
episodes.title: Retreat

episodes.synopsis: Kate must choose between one firm and the other. Frankie juggles two girlfriends. Alice has her first boyfriend, and Anne sits her down for the talk.
episodes.title: Red Handed

episodes.synopsis: Kate is depressed but finds a way to help Alice, who is navigating a milestone. Brad goads Anne into guest lecturing. Frankie becomes self-sufficient.
episodes.title: Spirit Animal

episodes.synopsis: Richard gives Kate some advice, and she takes it. Anne meets with an obsessive fan. Ian's meeting with producers is interrupted by an emergency.
episodes.title: Cuck

episodes.synopsis: Kate explores her medical issues and meets with a potential client. Frankie returns to familiar work. Anne and Lionel take on Brad's predator behavior.
episodes.title: Trash Panda

episodes.synopsis: Anne decides to expose a bad doctor. Nathan and Kate butt heads about a health scare. Sonia's heartbreak complicates her relationship with Ian and Zoe.
episodes.title: If Women Had to Give Birth

episodes.synopsis: Anne and Lionel's commitment ceremony brings friends and family together, but mid-party a guest uncovers a life-changing secret.
episodes.title: Look Back

episodes.synopsis: After Nathan's infidelity, Kate moves forward with a brand-new apartment, a brand-new business, a brand-new assistant -- and a brand-new baby.
episodes.title: Birth Daze

episodes.synopsis: In need of cash for her fledgling business, Kate considers bending her morals. Meanwhile, at Frankie Coyne Realty, the market's blowing up.
episodes.title: Of Rights and Men

episodes.synopsis: Kate juggles a tricky client -- and an insatiable Forrest. Jenny finds support at a moms' group, and Anne talks her way into a new job.
episodes.title: Daddy's Home

episodes.synopsis: Anne trains Alice for war on the streets, and Frankie helps Bianca prepare for motherhood. Kate comes face-to-face with an old foe.
episodes.title: Training Day

episodes.synopsis: Jenny throws Zoe a blowout birthday bash, and bad press ruins Kate's reputation. An overprotective Anne fears for her daughter's safety.
episodes.title: Stand for Something

episodes.synopsis: Charlie's school sends Kate home with an unpleasant assignment. Bianca gets bad news ... but Frankie might have a solution.
episodes.title: Narls in Charge

episodes.synopsis: Jenny gets a promotion, Alice gets revenge, and Frankie gets a look at Val's home life. Kate takes to the streets with a brilliant idea.
episodes.title: Revenge Fantasy

episodes.synopsis: Confessions come out of the woodwork when Kate, Anne, Frankie and Val take a memorable trip into the wild.
episodes.title: Girls' Trip

episodes.synopsis: Jenny leans in at work, Kate and Mike turn up the heat, and Frankie opens her heart. Anne takes a client's problems into her own hands.
episodes.title: Guns 'n' Deception

episodes.synopsis: Nathan steps in to help when Kate gets hit with a lawsuit. Elsewhere, Frankie wrestles with Bianca's faith, and Anne and Lionel double down on Alice.
episodes.title: Creamed

episodes.synopsis: Jenny brings Ian to the office, and Val puts Mel's skills to the test. Anne and Lionel host Brenna's parents for an explosive dinner.
episodes.title: Business Boyz

episodes.synopsis: Kate and Mike join forces for a client pitch, and Frankie finds herself playing mediator. Alice makes a desperate choice.
episodes.title: Two Paths

episodes.synopsis: Kate comes to a fork in the road, Anne learns the truth about Alice, and Ian shows Jenny the light. Val jumps at the chance for love.
episodes.title: What's It Gonna Be

episodes.synopsis: Kate faces her friends  and their judgement  in the wake of a big decision. With Alice in "activity jail," Anne pitches a parenting book.
episodes.title: Charade

episodes.synopsis: Frankie makes a bold move that Bianca might not be ready for. Lionel takes his daughter to work, and Kate clashes with Mike over a client.
episodes.title: Black Sheep

episodes.synopsis: A repentant Alice earns back her internship at Kate Foster PR, and Jenny makes an unsettling discovery. Frankie grows suspicious of Sean.
episodes.title: The Man in the Mexican Mask

episodes.synopsis: Kate confronts Mike, handles a crisis, then hosts a birthday dinner. Anne pushes through writer's block, and Jenny makes a play for equal pay.
episodes.title: No One's Coming

episodes.synopsis: While Nathan and Kate navigate their new living arrangement, Frankie and Juniper investigate Sean. A furtive search puts Anne's book in jeopardy.
episodes.title: To Lure a Squirrel

episodes.synopsis: A lice outbreak at camp adds an awkward layer to Kate's "40 Under 40" interview. Alice opens up to Anne, and Frankie hawks a house with a morbid past.
episodes.title: Lice

episodes.synopsis: Kate balances work and motherhood while Jenny battles backlash at the office. Bianca and Frankie get shocking news at the bank.
episodes.title: Bad Reputation

episodes.synopsis: As a frantic Kate searches for Charlie, Frankie seizes her chance for revenge. Anne and Lionel make a pivotal decision, and Jenny wins big at work.
episodes.title: Charlie and The Weed Factory

episodes.synopsis: Kate and the gang fly out to visit Anne, only to discover she's made some questionable new friends. Alice meets a cute boy on her first day at school.
episodes.title: The Carlsons Move to Calgary

episodes.synopsis: Kate feels the pressure to land a major new client. Anne's torn between ambition and fitting in. Frankie buys Rhoda a strange new pet.
episodes.title: Mamma Mia Meatboy

episodes.synopsis: Anne starts her new job, and Kate leans in to learn from Sloane. Jenny's secret office romance is a little bit different than she expected.
episodes.title: Pleasure Yourself

episodes.synopsis: Frankie hires three new agents to expand her business. Jenny confronts MCP about what he really wants. Kate introduces Anne to Sloane.
episodes.title: A Rat, Girl

episodes.synopsis: Anne's temper gets in the way of promoting her parenting book. Val's "empty" nest... isn't. And a quick fix at work leaves Kate feeling trapped.
episodes.title: Mother Knows Breast

episodes.synopsis: Anne's television debut goes off the rails. A disaster at work throws Frankie into a funk. Jenny's feelings for MCP might run deeper than she thought.
episodes.title: Finger in the Butt

episodes.synopsis: While Anne hides out at Val's, Kate slips on some fancy new boots to make it rain. Frankie takes responsibility for a workplace tragedy.
episodes.title: Launch Pad to Trash Hole

episodes.synopsis: Kate faces the consequences for her behavior, and Anne's surprised to see Lionel starring in a viral video. Frankie's on a mission to right her wrongs.
episodes.title: Punch Dad

episodes.synopsis: Anne enrolls Alice in a new school to protect her family's public image. Kate starts to question Sloane's ethics. Jenny gets everything she wants.
episodes.title: Blue Angel

episodes.synopsis: With everything on the line, Kate makes a major sacrifice. Anne gets surprising news. Jenny's lies finally catch up to her.
episodes.title: FACK
